{"tid":338280,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"傳 阿 Fred 解 凍 同 狐 狸 精 蕩 娃 何 硬 屍 斬 纜 ！","createTime":"2017-07-28T05:07:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T13:01:30.000Z","uid":53178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6ea19d23a1e0dff7dd431ab8f5e918a0a1e02363","tid":338280,"uid":53178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T05:07:48.000Z","msg":"鄭俊弘早前被指瞞住拍拖3年嘅未婚妻，同何雁詩拍拖，二人更喺機場高調拖手現身，當時何雁詩被指係小三，一度患情緒病，而鄭俊弘被網民封為「賤男」，形象插水，疑被大台掟咗入雪櫃，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">最近已偷偷「解凍」，鄭俊弘開始出番騷，不過工作量已大不如前，未知佢係咪為保事業，早前傳過佢刻意唔見女友何雁詩。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n今日有周刊指，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>鄭俊弘近排一心想洗底，少咗見何雁詩，今日有周刊指，何雁詩為人多疑，見同男友相處少，竟然多次上門查男友電話，又同鄭俊弘嘈交，搞到關係好僵</strong></span>，有傳何雁詩一向戀愛大過天，估計係黐身女友。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/28/130445_d1242bf5e4564a59fb08f57defef991c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F28%2F130445_d1242bf5e4564a59fb08f57defef991c.jpg&h=203ec443&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/28/130451_6036f21111bdfde450d27a04683df654.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F28%2F130451_6036f21111bdfde450d27a04683df654.jpg&h=222f510d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>狐 狸 精 蕩 婦 何 硬 屍 死 不 足 惜 ！ 一 撚 定 唔 會 俾 機 會 賤 男 阿 Fred 翻 身 ！</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e58fc83e9a2ce4bbc680663e3343d7cecabbd91b","tid":338280,"uid":48631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T05:18:17.000Z","msg":"牙醫走左想唔解凍牙fred都唔得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2379694fde74cdc08b6f3e80181bf9ac5f5e956","tid":33828